title: Captain Marvel to Battle Flerkens!
body:
Captain Marvel is just having a quiet night hanging out with Jessica Drew, aka Spider-Woman, when Manhattan is overrun by Flerkens in Marvel Action: Captain Marvel.


Marvel Action: Captain Marvel hails from writer Sam Maggs, artist Sweeney Boo, and colorist Brittany Peer. IDW Publishing’s Marvel Action imprint is aimed at middle grade readers, but I’m sure we can all agree that seeing Captain Marvel battle an army of fierce kitty-lookalikes sounds awesome.


Marvel Action: Captain Marvel #1 will release in August 2019 with a regular cover by Sweeney Boo and a special retailer incentive variant by Brianna Garcia.

(Cover Marvel Action: Captain Marvel #1 via IDW Publishing)
